Wieden + Kennedy, Inc.


                  Wieden + Kennedy, Inc. owns and operates advertising agency. The firm's services include brand building and television commercial production. It has additional offices in New York, New York; Sao Paulo, Brazil; London, the United Kingdom; Amsterdam, the Netherlands; Delhi, India; Shanghai, China; and Tokyo, Japan. The company was founded by Dan Wieden and David Kennedy in April 1982 and is headquartered in Portland, OR.                




Head of the Global World Cup & Olympic Campaigns

